gentleman who's phoned all the morning.

576
00:32:20,143 --> 00:32:21,218
What does he want?

577
00:32:21,318 --> 00:32:24,190
I don't know, Your Highness. But he
insists upon seeing you personally.

578
00:32:25,061 --> 00:32:26,698
Very well .. show him in.

579
00:32:39,516 --> 00:32:40,846
You wish to see me, Monsieur?

580
00:32:40,946 --> 00:32:42,855
Yes .. may I be seated?

581
00:32:45,289 --> 00:32:46,591
May I be permitted to say ..

582
00:32:46,832 --> 00:32:48,405
That the reports are not exaggerated.

583
00:32:48,832 --> 00:32:49,704
What reports?

584
00:32:49,943 --> 00:32:52,193
That you are the most beautiful,
the most gracious ..

585
00:32:52,396 --> 00:32:53,812
The best dressed woman in Paris.

586
00:32:53,928 --> 00:32:55,630
You come to pay me
compliments, Monsieur?

587
00:32:55,848 --> 00:32:57,219
Ah no, I came on business.

588
00:32:57,444 --> 00:32:58,476
The compliments ..

589
00:32:59,297 --> 00:33:00,723
Who could resist offering them?

590
00:33:01,036 --> 00:33:01,937
Your Highness.

591
00:33:02,643 --> 00:33:04,327
I plan to produce a revue.

592
00:33:04,885 --> 00:33:07,433
The most spectacular revue
that Paris has ever seen.

593
00:33:07,959 --> 00:33:09,690
How does that concern me, Monsieur?

594
00:33:09,945 --> 00:33:11,425
Ah, it concerns you intimately.

595
00:33:12,581 --> 00:33:15,777
This is to be a review
glorifying Parisian fashion.

596
00:33:16,382 --> 00:33:19,228
Your Highness, I plan
to make you the star in it.

597
00:33:19,456 --> 00:33:20,700
I am not amused, Monsieur.

598
00:33:21,393 --> 00:33:22,830
Please be good enough to retire.

599
00:33:23,295 --> 00:33:24,481
I have only just begun.

600
00:33:24,707 --> 00:33:27,202
Your Highness, I have an Idea
for an ostrich feather number.

601
00:33:27,302 --> 00:33:28,946
If you do not leave at once, Monsieur ..

602
00:33:29,242 --> 00:33:30,515
I shall ring for my butler.

603
00:33:30,695 --> 00:33:33,173
But this number Your Highness
will simply knock you eye out.

604
00:33:34,502 --> 00:33:35,477
How dare you.

605
00:33:35,577 --> 00:33:37,332
Come on now, Mabel. Be yourself.

606
00:33:38,582 --> 00:33:39,965
Well, well, well.

607
00:33:40,335 --> 00:33:41,967
How are things back in Hoboken?

608
00:33:43,319 --> 00:33:45,021
And I thought I was
getting away with it.

609
00:33:45,236 --> 00:33:47,907
Well, I must admit the peroxide had
me fooled for a little bit. But ..

610
00:33:48,323 --> 00:33:50,395
Mabel, I never forget a personality.

611
00:33:50,634 --> 00:33:51,583
[ Door knocks ]

612
