646
00:35:15,058 --> 00:35:16,951
No he won't. We let him
design the costumes.

647
00:35:17,205 --> 00:35:19,710
He wouldn't do it.
- Of course he will. You'll make him.

648
00:35:20,005 --> 00:35:21,520
The best-dressed woman in Paris.

649
00:35:22,052 --> 00:35:24,843
The greatest revue in a generation.
The triumph of the ostrich feather.

650
00:35:25,197 --> 00:35:26,228
The great Baroque.

651
00:35:26,328 --> 00:35:28,669
But what if I can't persuade him?
- Listen, dearie.

652
00:35:29,367 --> 00:35:31,666
You sold him the idea you were
a Grand Duchess, didn't you?

653
00:35:40,481 --> 00:35:42,155
You're just a piker, Ward.

654
00:35:42,411 --> 00:35:44,238
