709
00:38:33,635 --> 00:38:34,536
Your Highness.

710
00:38:39,038 --> 00:38:40,432
That will be all, Miss Lynn.

711
00:38:45,033 --> 00:38:46,449
Your Highness, Monsieur Baroque.

712
00:38:46,616 --> 00:38:48,061
