catching on in New York.

720
00:39:11,774 --> 00:39:14,259
Oh, that's only chickenfeed
compared to this racket.

721
00:39:15,277 --> 00:39:16,560
Get a load of that Duchess.

722
00:39:16,842 --> 00:39:18,964
Isn't she a honey?
- Yeah, sweet.

723
00:39:19,654 --> 00:39:21,520
Uhuh .. catty, catty.

724
00:39:24,843 --> 00:39:26,461
Why of all people, Savarin?

725
00:39:26,870 --> 00:39:28,481
He is no artist. He has no soul.

726
00:39:28,755 --> 00:39:31,151
Well, Senator Ward insists upon Savarin.

727
00:39:31,335 --> 00:39:32,450
Don't you, Senator?

728
00:39:35,412 --> 00:39:36,656
I say: don't you, senator?

729
00:39:38,099 --> 00:39:39,091
Why don't I what?

730
00:39:39,191 --> 00:39:41,193
The senator is just a
little hard of hearing.

731
00:39:41,987 --> 00:39:44,516
