- What's the matter, honey?

745
00:40:25,044 --> 00:40:27,423
I do wish he'd stick to
one racket at a time.

746
00:40:27,584 --> 00:40:28,880
Or one girl, huh?

747
00:40:31,389 --> 00:40:33,117
To whom shall I make this check pay out?

748
00:40:33,465 --> 00:40:34,704
To cash.

749
00:40:34,922 --> 00:40:35,620
Nash?

750
00:40:36,122 --> 00:40:36,766
Cash.

751
00:40:37,173 --> 00:40:39,192
I handle all the finances
for Senator Ward.

752
00:40:39,712 --> 00:40:40,709
And myself.

753
00:40:41,559 --> 00:40:42,231
Voila.

754
00:40:42,626 --> 00:40:43,891
Thank you, Mr Baroque.

755
00:40:44,206 --> 00:40:45,487
On behalf of the senator.

756
00:40:46,071 --> 00:40:48,463
You know, if I may say so, I think
we're all to be congratulated.

757
00:40:48,563 --> 00:40:49,899
Absolutely. Monsieur Nash.

758
00:40:50,064 --> 00:40:53,155
